* [[Watatsumi Shrine_(Kobe)|Watatsumi Shrines]] - Located in [[:en:Tarumi-ku, Kobe|Tarumi-ku, Kobe]], [[:en:Kobe|Kobe]], [[:en:Hyōgo Prefecture|Hyōgo Prefecture]]. It is a {{ill|Myōjin Taisha|ja|名神大社|lt=Shikinaisha Myōjin Taisha|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Myōjin Taisha|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} and a former {{ill|Kanpeichūsha|ja|官幣中社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanpeichūsha|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 近代社格制度|1=modern system of ranked Shinto shrines|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q712534}}. * {{ill|Kaijin Shrine (Toyooka)|ja|海神社 (豊岡市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaijin Shrine (Toyooka)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Toyooka, Hyōgo|Toyooka City]], Hyōgo Prefecture. It is a Shikinaisha Myōjin Taisha and a former {{ill|Village Shrine|ja|村社|1=Son-sha|qid=Q134917284}}{{efn|Former shrine rank|lt=Son-sha|1=modern system of ranked Shinto shrines|lt=Sonsha|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Village Shrine|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 近代社格制度|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q712534}}. * {{ill|Kaijin Shrine (Kinokawa)|ja|海神社 (紀の川市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaijin Shrine (Kinokawa)|qq=}} - Located in [[:en:Kinokawa, Wakayama|Kinokawa, Wakayama]], [[:en:Wakayama Prefecture|Wakayama Prefecture]]. It is a former {{ill|Prefectural Shrine|ja|県社|1=Prefectural Shrine|qid=Q90139226}}{{efn|Ken-sha|lt=Ken-sha|1=modern system of ranked Shinto shrines|lt=Kensha|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Prefectural Shrine|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 近代社格制度|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q712534}}. * {{ill|Kaijin Shrine (Nishinoshima)|ja|海神社 (西ノ島町)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaijin Shrine (Nishinoshima)|qq=|1=Kai Shrine|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11559097}} - Located in [[:en:Nishinoshima, Shimane|Nishinoshima, Shimane]], [[:en:Oki District|Oki District]], [[:en:Shimane Prefecture|Shimane Prefecture]]. It is a Shikinaisha Shōsha (minor shrine) and a former Village Shrine. * {{ill|Kaijin Shrine (Iki)|ja|海神社 (壱岐市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaijin Shrine (Iki)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Iki, Nagasaki|Iki City]], [[:en:Nagasaki Prefecture|Nagasaki Prefecture]]. It is a Shikinaisha Taisha and a former Village Shrine.
